OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will
OL,6,Fremain cloudy during the evening and
OL,7,Fthrough the night with outbreaks of
OL,8,Fheavy and perhaps thundery rain.
OL,9,FClearer, drier spells developing in
OL,10,Fthe west towards morning.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FCloudier at first with heavy,
OL,13,Fshowery overnight rain soon clearing.
OL,14,FThen bright or sunny spells and
OL,15,Fscattered showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
