OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FCloud
OL,6,Fand rain soon spreading east on
OL,7,FMonday. Cloudy on Tuesday with
OL,8,Foccasionally heavy rain or showers.
OL,9,FFurther showers or longer spells of
OL,10,Frain on Wednesday.
